  \cf5 Validation Boundaries\cf2 : Professional software validates at \cf5 boundaries\cf2  - \
  the points where data enters your system. In your app, there are two \
  critical boundaries: (1) the Session constructor (external data becomes \
   domain objects), and (2) file loading (text becomes objects). \
  Currently, both boundaries trust their inputs completely. Module 7 \
  teaches you to be defensive at these boundaries. \
